      <title>从零开始的个人Blog搭建</title>
      <link href="/2026/03/15/%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BABlog%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
      <url>/2026/03/15/%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BABlog%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Windows-PowerShell-从零搭建-Hexo-博客工作流程"><a href="#Windows-PowerShell-从零搭建-Hexo-博客工作流程" class="headerlink" title="Windows + PowerShell 从零搭建 Hexo 博客工作流程"></a>Windows + PowerShell 从零搭建 Hexo 博客工作流程</h1><h2 id="技术栈"><a href="#技术栈" class="headerlink" title="技术栈"></a>技术栈</h2><ul><li><p>Node.js</p></li><li><p>Git</p></li><li><p>Hexo</p></li><li><p>GitHub</p></li><li><p>GitHub Pages</p></li></ul><hr><h1 id="一、安装基础环境并配置镜像源"><a href="#一、安装基础环境并配置镜像源" class="headerlink" title="一、安装基础环境并配置镜像源"></a>一、安装基础环境并配置镜像源</h1><h2 id="1-安装-Node-js"><a href="#1-安装-Node-js" class="headerlink" title="1 安装 Node.js"></a>1 安装 Node.js</h2><p>下载 LTS 版本：</p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/">https://nodejs.org</a></p><p>安装完成后在 PowerShell 验证：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果能输出版本号说明安装成功。</p><p>在使用npm下载各种包之前，需先配置镜像源:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config set registry https://registry.npmmirror.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="2-安装-Git"><a href="#2-安装-Git" class="headerlink" title="2 安装 Git"></a>2 安装 Git</h2><p>下载：</p><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com</a></p><p>安装完成后验证：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="二、安装-Hexo-CLI"><a href="#二、安装-Hexo-CLI" class="headerlink" title="二、安装 Hexo CLI"></a>二、安装 Hexo CLI</h1><p>Hexo CLI 是 Hexo 的命令行工具。</p><p>在 PowerShell 中执行：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>验证安装：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果显示 Hexo 版本信息说明安装成功。</p><hr><h1 id="三、初始化博客项目"><a href="#三、初始化博客项目" class="headerlink" title="三、初始化博客项目"></a>三、初始化博客项目</h1><p>选择一个工作目录，例如：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd D:\</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建 Hexo 博客：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init ZesBlog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入博客目录：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ZesBlog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装依赖：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时目录结构大致如下：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ZesBlog</span><br><span class="line">│</span><br><span class="line">├─ _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">├─ package.json</span><br><span class="line">├─ source</span><br><span class="line">├─ themes</span><br><span class="line">└─ scaffolds</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="四、本地启动博客"><a href="#四、本地启动博客" class="headerlink" title="四、本地启动博客"></a>四、本地启动博客</h1><h2 id="1-生成静态页面"><a href="#1-生成静态页面" class="headerlink" title="1 生成静态页面"></a>1 生成静态页面</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>该命令会把 Markdown 内容生成静态 HTML。</p><hr><h2 id="2-启动本地服务器"><a href="#2-启动本地服务器" class="headerlink" title="2 启动本地服务器"></a>2 启动本地服务器</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>浏览器访问：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://localhost:4000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可看到博客页面。</p><hr><h1 id="五、创建文章"><a href="#五、创建文章" class="headerlink" title="五、创建文章"></a>五、创建文章</h1><p>新建文章：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &quot;first post&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Hexo 会自动生成文件：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source/_posts/first-post.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文章基本结构：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: First Post</span><br><span class="line">date: 2026-03-15</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>文章内容写在这里。</code></p><hr><h1 id="六、创建-GitHub-仓库"><a href="#六、创建-GitHub-仓库" class="headerlink" title="六、创建 GitHub 仓库"></a>六、创建 GitHub 仓库</h1><p>登录 GitHub，没有账号现建一个。</p><p>创建一个仓库：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">username.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zeszheng.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个仓库将用于托管博客。<br>SSH 链接复制下来,一会要用</p><hr><h1 id="七、安装部署插件"><a href="#七、安装部署插件" class="headerlink" title="七、安装部署插件"></a>七、安装部署插件</h1><p>Hexo 需要部署插件才能发布到 GitHub Pages。</p><p>安装：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="八、配置部署"><a href="#八、配置部署" class="headerlink" title="八、配置部署"></a>八、配置部署</h1><p>编辑博客根目录：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">_config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加部署配置：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">type: git</span><br><span class="line">repo: https://github.com/username/username.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将 <code>username</code> 替换为你的 GitHub 用户名。</p><hr><h1 id="九、部署博客"><a href="#九、部署博客" class="headerlink" title="九、部署博客"></a>九、部署博客</h1><p>执行：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>部署完成后访问：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https://username.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可看到你的博客。</p><hr><h1 id="十、日常写作工作流"><a href="#十、日常写作工作流" class="headerlink" title="十、日常写作工作流"></a>十、日常写作工作流</h1><p>日常使用 Hexo 的基本流程如下。</p><h2 id="1-创建文章"><a href="#1-创建文章" class="headerlink" title="1 创建文章"></a>1 创建文章</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &quot;post title&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="2-本地预览"><a href="#2-本地预览" class="headerlink" title="2 本地预览"></a>2 本地预览</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="3-发布博客"><a href="#3-发布博客" class="headerlink" title="3 发布博客"></a>3 发布博客</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="十一、总结"><a href="#十一、总结" class="headerlink" title="十一、总结"></a>十一、总结</h1><p>完整流程：</p><ol><li><p>安装 Node.js，配置镜像源 和 Git</p></li><li><p>安装 Hexo CLI</p></li><li><p>初始化 Hexo 项目</p></li><li><p>本地运行博客</p></li><li><p>创建 GitHub 仓库</p></li><li><p>配置部署插件</p></li><li><p>发布到 GitHub Pages</p></li></ol><p>之后日常写作只需：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可完成写作、预览和发布。</p>]]></content>
      
      
